Masire has been praised for promoting the social and economic well-being of Botswana during his 18-year reign. JOHANNESBURG Botswana s former president Ketumile Masire will be laid to rest on Thursday. Masire died last week at the age of 91 at a Gaborone hospital.The former head of state will be buried in his home village next to his late wife.Masire has been praised for promoting the social and economic well-being of Botswana during his 18-year reign.